quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  35,1,"Yettoore woodanii Alla, Tagu…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, Wa…óu…óo Malaa'ika'en nulaa…ďe, mar…ďe gabitanji(bibje) …ói …ói…ói, …ói tati e nayi. Himo …ďeyda ko O muuyi e tagu Makko ngun, tawde pellet, Alla ko hattan…óo kala huunde"
  35,2,"Kala yurmeende nde Alla udditani yim…ďe …ďen, jogitotoo…óo nde alaa; kala kadi ko O jogitii, accitoowo …óum alaa …ďaawo (jogitagol) Makko. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  35,3,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe! jantee neema Alla on e mon. Hara tagoowo ko woori Alla no woodi, mo no arsikira on ka kammu e ka leydi? Rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Kanko! E ko honno yiilirte…óon [e kaa goonga]"
  35,4,"Si …ďe fennii ma, pellet Nulaa…ďe (goo) fennanooma ado maa. Ko faade e Alla, woni ruttorde fiyakuuji …óin"
  35,5,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe! Anndee pellet fodoore Alla nden ko goonga. Wata nguurndam aduna hodu on, wata (seytaane) hodoowo on hodu on e fii Alla"
  35,6,"Pellet, seytaane ko ga√Īo wonani on. Haray jogitoree mo ga√Īo. Anndee ko o noddirta fedde makko nden, ko no …ďe jeydiree e yim…ďe dul…ďoowe ngen"
  35,7,"Hino woodani yeddu…ďe …ďen, lepte sa…ótu…óe. ∆Āeya gom…óim…ďe …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe, hino woodani …ďe haforaneede e njo…ďdi mawndi"
  35,8,"E ko on cu…óinanaa…óo golle mun bon…óe, hara himo yi'a …óe mo∆ī∆īu…óe? - Tawde pellet, Alla no majjina on Mo O muuyi, O fewna Mo O muuyi. Wata a tampinir hoore-maa, sunagol fii ma…ď…ďe. Pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo ko …ďe woni huuwude"
  35,9,"Ko Alla woni wurtu…óo keneeli …óin, …ói sogga duule, Men yarnira …óum leydi yoorundi; Men wuurnitira …óum leydi ndin, …ďaawo ndi yoorude. Ko wano non ummital ngal"
  35,10,"Kala taw…óo ko teddungal faalaa (yo o …óa…ď…ďir Alla), tawde ko Alla jeyi teddungal ngal fow: ko ka Makko woni ko konngol laa…ďungol ∆īawata, golle mo∆ī∆īe …óen …ďamta ngol. ∆Āen fewjoo…ďe boneeji, hino woodani …ďe lepte sa…ótu…óe. Pewje …ďen …óen, ko bonay …óe"
  35,11,"Ko Alla tagiri on e mbulbuldi, refti e to…ď…ďere (maniiyu), refti O wa…ói on nooneeji. Deyel saawataa, ngel lelnataa kadi, si wanaa e anndal Makko. Wuurnaa…óo wuurnetaake, …óuytetaake kadi e nguurndam makko, si wanaa no e deftere. Pellet, …óum ko newanii …óum Alla"
  35,12,"Maaje …óen …ói…ói fotataa: [Ndiyam] goo …óoo …óam, ko wel…óam, laa…ďungo, newiingo njaram mun, ngoo …óaa, ko lan…óam haa…óu…óam. Hi…óon √Īaama e kala majjam, teewu keccu, hi…óon yaltina kadi hen, cu…óaari ndi …ďoornoto…óon. Hi…óa yi'a laa…óe …óen no awja e maggo, fii yo on …óa…ď…ďiron e …ďural Makko. Belajoo on yettay [Mo]"
  35,13,"Himo naada jemma on e der √Īalorma on, O naada √Īalorma on e nder jemma on. O elti kadi naange ngen e lewru ndun. Kala mun no doga haa e lajal innaangal. Ko On moo…óon woni Alla, Joomi mon: Ko Kanko Laamu woodani. ∆äiya …ói noddoton gaanin Makko, …ói jeytaa yeru gorol tamara"
  35,14,"Si on noddu …ói, …ói nanataa noddaandu mon; hay si …ói nanoy, …ói jaabitotaako on. √Ďalnde Darngal, …ói yeddoyay sirku mon on. Alaa habroowo ma, wano Humpitii…óo On"
  35,15,"Ko onon yo yim…ďe, ko onon woni hatonjim…ďe e Alla …ďen, Alla kan, ko Kanko woni Galo Yettinii…óo On"
  35,16,"Si O yi…óii, O na…ďa on, O adda tagu hesu"
  35,17,∆äum wonaali sattu…óum ka Alla
  35,18,"Wonki ronndotaako doŇčgal wonkii goo. Hay si teddiraaki [junuubi] kin noddii e ronndaneede, ki ronndantaake hay huunde, hay si ko …ďadondiraa…óo Anndu ko jertintaa [nana waaju], ko …ďen huliroo…ďe Joomi mun ka wirnii, …ďe √Īii…ďi e Julde. Kala on la…ď…ďinii…óo, haray ko hoore makko o woni la…ď…ďinanaade. Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde nden"
  35,19,Bun…óo e yi'oowo fotataa
  35,20,wanaa ni…ďe …óen e ndaygu ngun
  35,21,wanaa …óowdi ndin e henndu wulndu ndun
  35,22,"Wanaa kadi wuur…ďe …ďen fotata e maay…ďe …ďen. Pellet, Alla no nanina on Mo O muuyani. Wanaa an [Nulaa…óo], woni naninoowo, won…ďe ka genaale …ďen"
  35,23,"An a wonaali, si wanaa jertinoowo"
  35,24,"Pellet, Men nulirii ma goonga, ko a wewlinoowo e jertinoowo. Alaa e mofte, si wanaa jertinoowo fe∆ī∆īii e ma…ď…ďe"
  35,25,"Si …ďe fennii ma, hari adinoo…ďe …ďe …ďen fenniino (Nulaa…ďe mun), fewndo …ďen Nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe addannoo …ďanngannduyeeji, e ∆äeri e Deftere ndayginoore"
  35,26,Refti nanngitir mi yeddu…ďe …ďen (halakuyee). Taskii no lepte An …óen wa…ótinirnoo
  35,27,"E a tinaali wonnde Alla jippinirii ndiyam ka kammu? Men fu…óiniri …óam dim…óe seertu…óe noone. Hino ka pelle, …óate daneeje e bo…óeeje seertyu…óe noone, e pete …ďaleeje"
  35,28,"Hino e yim…ďe …ďen, e daabeeji …óin, e neemoraa…ói …óin, …ói nooneeji mun kadi luutondiri. Anndu ko hulata Alla e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, ko anndu…ďe …ďen. Pellet, Alla ko Foolu…óo, Haforoowo"
  35,29,"∆Āen janngoo…ďe Deftere Alla nden, …ďe √Īii…ďi e julde, …ďe nafqii ko Men arsiki …ďe kon gunndoo e kene, hi…ďe jortii njulaaku ngu sontataa"
  35,30,"Fii no [Alla] hunnirana …ďe njo…ďdiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin, O …ďeyda …ďe e …ďural Makko ngal. Kanko, ko O Haforoowo, Annditanoowo [on]"
  35,31,"Kon ko Men wahayini e maa…óa e Deftere nden, ko …óum woni goonga, gom…óinde e …óen won…óe yeeso mayre. Pellet, Alla ko Humpitii…óo Rentu…óo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen"
  35,32,"Refti Men ronini Deftere nden, …ďen …ďe Men su…ďii e jeyaa…ďe Amen. Hino e ma…ď…ďe too√Īu…ďe hoore-mun, hino e ma…ď…ďe hakindin…óo, hino e ma…ď…ďe foolondiroo…ďe e mo∆ī∆īereeji, duŇčayee Alla; ko …óum woni …ďural mawnungal ngal"
  35,33,"Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal, …ói naatata e mun, hara hi…ďe cu…óiree ton, jawe kaŇčŇče e kaalise e lu‚Äôu-lu‚Äôu; comci ma…ď…ďe …óin ton, ko sooyi"
  35,34,"∆Āe wi'a: \"Yettoore woodanii Alla, On ittan…óo en suno. Pellet, Joomi men, ko Haforoowo, Warjotoo…óo"
  35,35,"On weernir…óo en …ďural Makko ngal, e galle √Īii…ďal, tampere (woo) he…ďataa en ton, wanaa ronkere he…ďata en ton"
  35,36,"Yeddu…ďe …ďen kan, ko Yiite Jahannama woodani …ďen; maayde √Īaawetaake e ma…ď…ďe, sakko …ďe maaya, …ďe hoynantaake kadi lepte magge …óen. Ko wano nii Men yo…ďitirta kala yeddu…óo"
  35,37,"Hara hi…ďe ooloo nder ton […ďe wi'a]: \"Joomi amen, yaltin men; men golla mo∆ī∆īere, hara wonah ko men gollaynoo kon\". [O jaaboo …ďe]: \"E men wuurnaano on yeru ko waajitotoo…óo waajitoranoo e mun? Jertinoowo kadi ari e mon? Awa mee…óee, sabu faabo alanaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  35,38,"Pellet, Alla ko Anndu…óo wirnii…ói kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Ko O Anndu…óo ko suu…óii e …ďer…óe"
  35,39,"Ko Kanko woni wa…óu…óo on lontii…ďe ka leydi. Kala yeddu…óo, ko e makko lorra geddi makko yantata. Yeddugol heefer…ďe …ďen, …ďeydataa …ďe ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa tikkere. Yeddugol …ďeydataa heefer…ďe …ďen, si wanaa hayrere"
  35,40,"Maaku: \"E on yi'ii rendii…ói mon rewoton gaanin Alla …óin? Hollee lam ko …ói tagi ka leydi. Kaa hi…ói mari ge…ďal e [tagugol] kammuuli …óin? Kaa Men addan …ďe Deftere, nde …ďe woni e …ďanndannduyee mun? Si ko woni, too√Īoo…ďe …ďen alaa e fodude yoga ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa hodo"
  35,41,"Pellet, ko Alla jogitii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, fii wata …ói dirtu. Hay si …ói dirtayno, hay gooto jogitotaako …ói e …ďaawo Makko. O laatike Mu√Ī√Īii…óo, Haforoowo"
  35,42,"∆Āe woodndiri Alla, hattirde e goondooje ma…ď…ďe, wonnde si jertinoowo arii e ma…ď…ďe, pellet, …ďe wonay …ďur…ďe feewude wootere e mofte …óen. Nde jertinoowo non arunoo e ma…ď…ďe, …óum …ďeydaali …ďe, si wanaa wo…ó…óitagol"
  35,43,"[∆Āe wa…óiri …óum] mawnintinaare ka keydi, e pewje …ďen…óe. Pewje bon…óe …óen non huu…ďitataa, si wanaa jom-mun'en. Hara hi…ďe sabbitii, si wanaa sunna (Alla) on e adinoo…ďe …ďen? A he…ďantaa sunna Alla on battiigu, a he…ďantaa sunna Alla waylir…óum"
  35,44,"E …ďee yiilaaki ka leydi, …ďe taskoo ko honno battane adinoo…ďe …ďen wonirnoo? Hari no …ďuri …ďe tii…óude doole. Alla siforaali wonnde go…ó…óum no ronkina Mo ka kammuuli maa ka leydi. Tawde pellet, ko O Anndu…óo, Hattan…óo"
  35,45,"Si tawno Alla nanngitirayno yim…ďe …ďen ko …ďe faggitorii kon, O accataano ruugayngel e dow mayri. Ko woni tun, Himo nennitana …ďe haa e lajal anndaa ngal. Si lajal ma…ď…ďe ngal hewtii, [O nanngay …ďe], tawde pellet, Alla ko Reenu…óo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen"